'''Azure Spaceport''' was an [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]] base situated on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Azure/Legends|Azure]]. Commanded by the [[Lutrillian/Legends|Lutrillian]] [[Solomahal/Legends|Solomahal]], a [[General/Legends|General]] of the Republic, it was [[Battle of Azure Spaceport|destroyed]] in an effort to keep the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]] from acquiring a codebreaker.<ref name="SOTJ">[[Secrets of the Jedi (novel)|''Secrets of the Jedi'']]</ref>

